Parent: EPIC: Fix Security Vulnerabilities (Synaxis-7gf0)

Fix Blocking Calls in Service Layer

## Problem
Service methods synchronously block on async I/O operations.

## Common Patterns
- Calling .Result on external API calls
- Using Task.WaitAll without async
- Synchronous wrappers around async code

## Location Pattern
- src/*/Application/Services/*.cs
- Domain service implementations

## Required Fix
```csharp
// Current (blocking):
public void ProcessOrder(Order order)
{
    var payment = _paymentService.ChargeAsync(order).Result;
    var notification = _emailService.SendAsync(order).Result;
}

// Fixed:
public async Task ProcessOrderAsync(Order order)
{
    var payment = await _paymentService.ChargeAsync(order);
    var notification = await _emailService.SendAsync(order);
}
```

## Verification Steps
- Audit all service method signatures
- Replace void methods returning void with Task
- Add Async suffix to async methods
- Verify no sync-over-async patterns

