Parent: EPIC: Fix Async/Await Anti-patterns (Synaxis-ebf0)

Fix Blocking Calls in API Controllers

## Problem
Controllers use .Result or improper async patterns instead of async/await.

## Location Pattern
- src/*/WebApi/Controllers/*.cs
- Middleware components

## Required Fix
```csharp
// Current (blocking):
[HttpGet]
public IActionResult GetItems()
{
    var items = _service.GetAllAsync().Result;
    return Ok(items);
}

// Fixed:
[HttpGet]
public async Task<IActionResult> GetItems()
{
    var items = await _service.GetAllAsync();
    return Ok(items);
}
```

## Verification Steps
- All controller actions should return Task<IActionResult>
- No .Result calls in controller methods
- No async void methods

